quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  7,1,Alif Laam Meem Saad
  7,2,"Yeh ek kitab hai jo tumhari taraf nazil ki gayi hai, pas (aey Muhammad), tumhare dil mein issey koi jhijak na ho, iske utaarne ki garz yeh hai ke tum iske zariye se (munkireen ko) darao aur iman laney waley logon ko yaad dihani ho"
  7,3,"Logon, jo kuch tumhare Rubb ki taraf se tumpar nazil kiya gaya hai uski pairwi karo aur apne Rubb ko chodh kar dusre sarparaton ki pairwi na karo, magar tum naseehat kam hi maante ho"
  7,4,"Kitni hi bastiyan hain jinhein humne halaak kardiya, unpar hamara azaab achanak raat ke waqt toot pada, ya din dahade aise waqt aaya jab woh aaraam kar rahey thay"
  7,5,Aur jab hamara azaab unpar aa gaya to unki zubaan par iske siwa koi sadaa na thi ke waqayi hum zalim thay
  7,6,Pas yeh zaroor hokar rehna hai ke hum un logon se baaz-purs karein jinki taraf humne paigambar bheje hain aur paigambaron se bhi puchein (ke unhon ne paigaam rasani ka farz kahan tak anjaam diya aur unhein iska kya jawab mila)
  7,7,Phir hum khud purey ilm ke saath saari sargushist (whole account) unke aagey pesh kardenge. Aakhir hum kahin gayab to nahin thay
  7,8,"Aur wazan us roz ain e haqq hoga, jinke padley bhaari hongey wahi falaah payenge"
  7,9,"Aur jinke padley halke rahenge wahi apne aap ko khasarey (nuksan) mein mubtila karne waley hongey, kyunke woh hamari aayat ke saath zalimana bartao karte rahey thay"
  7,10,Humne tumhein zameen mein ikhtiyarat ke saath basaya aur tumhare liye yahan samaan e zeist faraham kiya Magar tumlog kam hi shukar-guzar hotey ho
  7,11,"Humne tumhari takhleeq (creation) ki ibteda ki, phir tumhari surat banayi, phir farishton se kaha Adam ko sajda karo. Is hukm par sabne sajda kiya magar Iblis sajda karne walon mein shamil na hua"